    • Method Detail

      • reduce

        public void reduce(int i,
          byte x)
        Reduce the given byte into the given array element of this shared variable.

        The item field's element at index i and the argument x are combined together using the bitwise Boolean and operation, and the result is stored in the item field's element at index i.

        Overrides:
        reduce in class ByteArrayVbl
        Parameters:
        i - Array index.
        x - Byte.
